{"tid":330482,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"連登仔技能發動 認出一個字可拎走10萬獎金","createTime":"2017-07-21T09:07:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-21T10:32:40.000Z","uid":39501,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"22853515d3380445a56701a1be958514511be145","tid":330482,"uid":39501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T09:07:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/21/170449_439a4e1f18101de3d65c8a3dcada1c57.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F21%2F170449_439a4e1f18101de3d65c8a3dcada1c57.jpg&h=ae121717&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n認字可以拿10萬元人民幣（下同，約11.5萬港元）？中國文字博物館發佈公告，列出一些至今仍未能破解、未釋讀的甲骨文，指要是有民眾能認出這些文字，並通過專家委員會鑑定通過，每個字獎10萬元。<br />\n位於河南安陽的中國文字博物館指出，目前仍有3,500個甲骨文單字未能破譯，破譯甲骨文的工作正處於樽頸期，破譯一個字都是攻堅戰，所以決定公佈待破解的文字，希望各界可以協助破解。<br />\n不過，要拿到這筆獎金並不容易，凡屬主觀臆測、缺乏科學依據的都一律不予參評，凡有弄虛作假、抄襲剽竊等，一經查實都會被立即取消參評資格。參加者的結果要經過專家委員會鑑定通過，才能發放獎金；如果對存爭議甲骨文作出新的釋讀、並經專家委員會鑑定通過的研究成果，單字獎勵5萬元（約5.9萬港元）。<br />\n<br />\n北京青年報<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20170721&amp;s=10793096&amp;a=56982839 \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170721%26s%3D10793096%26a%3D56982839%20&d=n7P4D0%2BhRwhYbBmgpuBG%2BE%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=7909acd4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170721%26s%3D10793096%26a%3D56982839%20&h=3d5478fc\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20170721&amp;s=10793096&amp;a=56982839 </a>"},{"pid":"7ac4100faf90f64d8c908b3056b62ec23f1f18c8","tid":330482,"uid":28515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T09:30:09.000Z","msg":"其實唔難"},{"pid":"6c0b02f38ab565357c53414bbe59434e0fc77681","tid":330482,"uid":96874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T10:04:31.000Z","msg":"可能係啲冇楷書寫法嘅字"},{"pid":"d676ae40e46f50de54c2ce911cb631489e8977f4","tid":330482,"uid":50041,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T10:07:27.000Z","msg":"會唔會果d字已經失傳左，現代根本無左呢隻字"},{"pid":"ac6a4fe2ebf76d27a787ce57c4e11046f5316e09","tid":330482,"uid":99028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T10:20:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d27e755b735cb3a56706d62cfe6bbb3ff92388d0","tid":330482,"uid":52942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T10:26:46.000Z","msg":"尾二仲唔係死者蘇生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db133e31c9f7e309cb03b7c1c5fcc685366dbe1d","tid":330482,"uid":86723,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T10:32:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/21/183217_85a9a1d613b4d2710d9f576ec3790cb6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F21%2F183217_85a9a1d613b4d2710d9f576ec3790cb6.jpg&h=9b2d6110&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/21/183223_147973670fce6acf6656e3cfed69c3ab.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F21%2F183223_147973670fce6acf6656e3cfed69c3ab.jpg&h=af8041e6&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}